metadata.name: Ottey Otters #0001
metadata.description: Ottey Otters is a collection of 3000 unique and lovable Otter NFTs available on the Ethereum blockchain. Owning an Ottey Otter unlocks the potential for future drops, real life plushies associated with an NFT, charity donations and much, much more. Come and join the community over at https://otteyotters.io
